name: Buy the dip , Sell the rip
description: Dataset taken from the TradingView. It is prepared with the users daily ideas on specific crypto currency pair charts (candlestick chart). A .js tool developed and used for downloading bulk images from the website. Python libraries (PIL and scipy.misc) used for bulk image resize and crop. Training process included the triangle patterns (descending , ascending ,symmetrical) , rising wedge, falling wedge and pennant patterns. I used stylegan2-ada repository for training process.
